divs: Sighting DetailsI just went to take a photo of the sky light [easterly position] as the sun was coming up, but still a while to go. My camera flashed and I thought I got a star in the photo. I snapped another and then looked at it inside, there was an object on both of the photos. One closer than the other. I went back outside on the deck, but nothing was in the sky. Have attached below 2 photos and one enlargment. Thanks. Carol Pappas.
